coza.opencollab.synthesis.service.api

Class ErrorCodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • coza.opencollab.synthesis.service.api.ErrorCodes

  • public class ErrorCodes
extends Object
    The error code manager.

    Error Code Ranges:

    1. 1000's: This is exceptions on the server
    2. 2000's: This is normal flow problems like login details that are not valid.
    3. 3000's: Admin tool
    4. 4000's: Client base and tools
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    OpenCollab
